Classes needed: 

abstract class Player
class MachinePlayer extends Player
class Board
class Move

Modules:

1) determine if a move is valid
boolean isValidMove(Move m)
2) generate a list of valid moves
int[][] validMoves(Board b)
3) establish connections with chips of same color

4) identify if network exists
boolean hasValidNetwork(Board b)
5) scoring and evaluating a board
int evaluateBoard(Board b)
6) performing a game search tree and pruning
Move chooseMove(int searchDepth)
int alphaBetaPrune(int alpha, int beta)

